Enum Class AlertCondition

Object
Enum<AlertCondition>
com.zebra.sdk.settings.AlertCondition
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<AlertCondition>, Constable
public enum AlertCondition extends Enum<AlertCondition>
Enumeration of the various printer alert conditions which can be set on Zebra Printers.
